   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="uoedh_hl_h.3185_1.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <address rend="letterhead">
                  <addrLine>The Royal Hotel,</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>Weymouth.</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>TELEPHONE No. 262.</addrLine>
               </address>
               <figure>
                  <figDesc>Top left corner: A printed black image of a lion lying in profile, facing
                     left.</figDesc>
               </figure>
               <dateline>
                  <date when="1920-07-06">July 6. <note hand="unknown">1920</note></date>
               </dateline>

               <salute>My dear friend:</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>I hope you &amp; <persName ref="#ps:FlorenceHardy">F.</persName> were not very tired
               after our charming &amp; interesting expedition. It was delightful to see so much in
               one afternoon. I hope that <hi rend="underline">Thursday</hi> afternoon will be as
               lovely as this one has <pb n="2" facs="uoedh_hl_h.3185_2.jpg"/> turned out, after the
               drenching morning. The sea has been a lovely peacock-blue. –</p>
            <p>I shall hope to arrive with <persName ref="#ps:AnnaHirschmann">Anna</persName> at the
               Museum at 2 – (or very soon afterward,) on <hi rend="underline">Thursday</hi>. –</p>

            <p><persName ref="#ps:FlorenceHardy">Florence</persName>'s bright nosegay from
                        <choice><abbr>y<hi rend="superscript"
                  >r</hi>.</abbr><expan>your</expan></choice>
               <pb n="3" facs="uoedh_hl_h.3185_3.jpg"/> garden makes a cheerful spot of colour in my
               window. It was so kind of her to bring me those flowers –</p>

            <p>Of <hi rend="underline">course no answer is expected to this</hi> - </p>

            <p>Thank you for showing me so much that was interesting –</p>

            <closer>
               <salute>always <choice><abbr>yr</abbr>
                     <expan>your</expan></choice> friend</salute>
               <signed>FloH</signed>
            </closer>
            <postscript>
               <p><choice><abbr>affec.</abbr>
                     <expan>affectionate</expan></choice> greeting to Wessex!</p>
            </postscript>

         </div>
      </body>
